text:
Done. Usage:

```
&lt;!-- Simple --&gt;
&lt;tq-page-header title="Locations"&gt;&lt;/tq-page-header&gt;

&lt;!-- With action button --&gt;
&lt;tq-page-header title="Locations" subtitle="Manage your service locations" icon="📍" count="5"&gt;
&lt;tq-button slot="actions" variant="primary" icon="➕" onclick="LocationsView.showCreateModal()"&gt;Add Location&lt;/tq-button&gt;
&lt;/tq-page-header&gt;

&lt;!-- Multiple actions --&gt;
&lt;tq-page-header title="Work Orders" count="12"&gt;
&lt;tq-button slot="actions" variant="secondary" icon="📥"&gt;Export&lt;/tq-button&gt;
&lt;tq-button slot="actions" variant="primary" icon="➕"&gt;Create Work Order&lt;/tq-button&gt;
&lt;/tq-page-header&gt;
```
Responsive — stacks vertically on mobile with full-width buttons. The sub-agent will use this in all the view migrations.
